How to add new maven project?
1. In intellj, new project and choose create directory (for main/test structure)
2. Search in mvn site for the dependance and past to pom.xml <dependancies> </..>  section.
3. Question: I need to go to module settings(ctrl + down arrow) and add dependance library from maven and search to refresh.
   Why do I need do this?

   Similarly to gradle.
